NFO Viewer 3000
===============

 * Bump PyGTK dependency to 2.16
   - Use attributes instead of markup in preferences-dialog.ui
   - Use gtk.show_uri instead of nfoview.util.browse_url
 * Bump PyGobject dependency to 2.14
   - gobject.set_application_name(_("NFO Viewer"))
   - gobject.set_prgname("nfoview")
 * Get link and visited link colors from GTK+ theme
 * Make hyperlinks activatable by keyboard
